      <title>尽管大型科技公司不断支出，人工智能硬件股票仍遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ai-hardware-stocks-get-pummeled-even-as-big-tech-keeps-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于半导体和其他人工智能计算硬件制造商来说，好消息是：科技巨头计划继续投入巨资。坏消息是投资者在这个财报季更难给人留下深刻印象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ai-hardware-stocks-get-pummeled-even-as-big-tech-keeps-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI 芯片预测低于预期后 AMD 股价下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amd-gives-tepid-forecast-amid-weak-demand-for-gaming-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 的股价下跌了 8.1%，此前这家芯片制造商对人工智能处理器的预测令人失望，该市场目前由 Nvidia 公司主导，利润丰厚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amd-gives-tepid-forecast-amid-weak-demand-for-gaming-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Z 世代倾向购物，Pinterest 飙升至 2020 年以来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinterest Inc. 公布的第一季度销售额和用户增长超出了华尔街的预期，这得益于其进军购物领域和对 Z 世代用户的关注，该公司股价创下三年多以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
